  "title": "Production Operator / Checker & Packer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description &amp; requirement:</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>• Loading / Unloading machines.<br>\n• Folding, packing &amp; tagging of Laundry/Linen.<br>\n• Setting up, monitoring, and maintaining machines and equipment used in the production lines.<br>\n• Labelling &amp; packing of goods.<br>\n• Supporting production in daily outputs.<br>\n• Perform inventory and housekeeping<br>\n• Performing any other duties as assigned by the Company.<br>\n• Pulls &amp; packs products based on the daily orders.<br>\n• Meets specifics of customer orders in a timely manner.<br>\n• Monitors product quality frequently, reporting problems to mitigate safety issues.</p>\n<p>• Singaporean, SPR are welcome to apply.</p>",
